3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper discusses the design of an optimal encoder, channel, and decoder, which is a common concept in machine learning. 
4. cs.SP (Signal Processing) - The paper deals with the problem of optimal estimation of time-varying multidimensional Gauss-Markov processes, which is a topic in signal processing. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper uses the developed theory to design filters for multidimensional processes, which can be applied to multimedia data such as images and videos.
